                            	  1021: * ===== The SIZE function returns the size of free memory in D0.
                            	  1022: *
00:0001128E 20390000614A    	  1023: SIZE	MOVE.L	VARBGN,D0	get the number of free bytes...
00:00011294 90B900006146    	  1024: 	SUB.L	TXTUNF,D0	between 'TXTUNF' and 'VARBGN'
00:0001129A 4E75            	  1025: 	RTS			return the number in D0
