                            	  1455: *
                            	  1456: * ===== Convert the character in D0 to upper case
                            	  1457: *
00:00011664 B03C0061        	  1458: TOUPPER CMP.B	#'a',D0         is it < 'a'?
00:00011668 6500000E        	  1459: 	BCS	TOUPRET
00:0001166C B03C007A        	  1460: 	CMP.B	#'z',D0         or > 'z'?
00:00011670 62000006        	  1461: 	BHI	TOUPRET
